Walls have eyes: How researchers observe you on Facebook
Before he became the new face of far-right extremism in Europe, Anders Behring Breivik was just one of many guys who broadcast their anti-immigration opinions online.
On Monday, Breivik, who has confessed to being involved in a shooting spree in Norway in July that killed 77 people, had his first public court hearing.
